cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and sentence representation. The use of neural models and machine learning techniques also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The experiments on sentence classification and machine translation suggest that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as these sub-categories often deal with similar tasks.
